title: How About That Ending Though?
review: Let me start of by saying, What kind of ending was that! What a waste of time and film. The story started of alright then fell flat all the way down from the middle to the end. I rather watch Harry potter go camping for about an hour again then watch Lobster again. That is my review, now lets discuss the joys of always hitting your toe in the corner of the door and how much you try to not let it get to you. Where was I going with this?
